The software that allows you to browse the internet on your Dreamcast. There were 3 made PlanetWeb being the american version. It used the Dreamcast's dial-up capabilities to surf the web.

The PlanetWeb Browser allowed not only access to the web but also allowed access to Java, uploads, and movies.
